you need .NET SDK 6.0 or newer

command:

- dotnet build
- dotnet run <sourceFolder> <replicaFolder> <intervalInSeconds> <logFilePath>
  sourceFolder : Path of the source folder (to be synchronized).
  replicaFolder : Path of the replica folder (where the synchronization will be performed).
  intervalInSeconds : Time interval between each synchronization (in seconds).
  logFilePath : Path of the file where the synchronization operations will be logged.
